abstract: >-
  A rigorous evidence-based methodology system for analyzing
  undeciphered Minoan Bronze Age inscriptions (c.1800-1450 BCE)
  using principles derived from the successful Linear B decipherment.
  Implements the Kober Method, multi-hypothesis testing, and
  anchor-based expansion with calibrated confidence levels.
